name: Starcounter Under the Hood
tagline: Home Page for Open Source Contributors
body:
### Welcome!

The GitHub Starcounter project contains source code for Starcounter contributors. The Starcounter DBMS will be made available under a Dual License. 

Currently, Starcounter 1.0 is only available under a Commercial License. However, the upcoming version 2.0 will be free for open source projects, personal projects (software owned by a single individual) and non-commercial projects.
